title: Parmesan Chicken Schnitzels & Capsicum Relish with Radish Slaw
description: There’s a way to jazz up any chicken schnitzel and that’s a sprinkling of cheese. Add sharp Parmesan to the crumb
so you don’t miss out on any flavour. If you’re feeling like going the extra mile, try dipping these schnitzels in a
smokey capsicum relish.

